                      "runs": [
                        {"type": "text", "text": "I can contribute a section on digital assessment tools that I've been researching. This could include platforms like Peergrade, Coursera's peer assessment system, and custom LMS solutions."}
                      ]
                    },
                    "suggestedChange": {
                      "runs": [
                        {"type": "text", "text": "Assessment in collaborative environments requires careful consideration of both individual contributions and group outcomes. Effective collaborative assessment strategies include:\n\n**Individual Accountability**: Use peer evaluation forms, individual reflections, and role-specific deliverables to assess each member's contribution.\n\n**Group Process Assessment**: Evaluate how well the group collaborates through observation checklists, group self-assessments, and communication logs.\n\n**Product Assessment**: Assess the final collaborative output using rubrics that weight both content quality and evidence of collaboration.\n\n**Digital Assessment Tools**: Platforms like Peergrade and integrated LMS peer assessment features can streamline the evaluation process and provide valuable analytics on collaboration patterns."}
